    <cas:Sofa xmi:id="1" sofaNum="1" sofaID="_InitialView" mimeType="text" sofaString="[8 August 2021, Bangladesh] One in ten households reported problems in accessing general healthcare services during the pandemic: The respondents were asked whether they faced any problem during the lockdown in accessing general healthcare services. One in ten households (9.9%) stated that they faced problems during getting treatment from hospitals. The problems include lack of sufficient doctors (70.2%), lack of sufficient nurse (39.6%), lack of medical equipment (38.8%), lack of medicine (38.0%), lack of beds (26.1%) and higher fees of doctors (20.4%). They also faced the unwillingness of doctors to provide treatment (23.3%), the unwillingness of hospitals to admit patients (20.0%) and bribery (13.9%). People from rural areas complained more about the lack of doctors (75.0% vs. 63.8%) and nurses (42.9% vs. 35.2%), adequate medical equipment (40.0% vs. 37.1%), beds (29.3% vs. 21.9%) and increase of doctor’s fees (23.6% vs.16.2%) compared to people from urban areas"/>
    <cas:View sofa="1" members="8 19 24 29 34 39 44 57 70 83 96 109 122 135 148 161 174 187 200 213 226 239 252 265 278 291 304 317 330 343 356 369 382 395 408 421 434 447 460 473 486 499 512 525 538 551 564 577 590 603 616 629 642 655 668 681 694 707 720 733 746 759 772 785 798 811 824 837 850 863 876 889 902 915 928 941 954 967 980 993 1006 1019 1032 1045 1058 1071 1084 1097 1110 1123 1136 1149 1162 1175 1188 1201 1214 1227 1240 1253 1266 1279 1292 1305 1318 1331 1344 1357 1370 1383 1396 1409 1422 1435 1448 1461 1474 1487 1500 1513 1526 1539 1552 1565 1578 1591 1604 1617 1630 1643 1656 1669 1682 1695 1708 1721 1734 1747 1760 1773 1786 1799 1812 1825 1838 1851 1864 1877 1890 1903 1916 1929 1942 1955 1968 1981 1994 2007 2020 2033 2046 2059 2072 2085 2098 2111 2124 2137 2150 2163 2176 2189 2202 2215 2228 2241 2254 2267 2280 2293 2306 2319 2332 2345 2358 2371 2384 2397 2410 2423 2436 2449 2462 2475 2488 2501 2514 2527 2540 2553 2566 2579 2592 2605 2618 2623 2628 2633 2638 2685 2690 2695 2700 2705 2745 2790 2750 2795 2755 2800 2760 2785 2765 2780 2770 2775 2847 2852 2857 2862 2867 2872 2898 2903 2908 2937 2927 2932 2956 2961 2966 2985 2990 2995 3014 3019 3024 2643 2650 2657 2664 2671 2678 2710 2717 2724 2731 2738 2805 2812 2826 2819 2833 2840 2877 2884 2891 2913 2920 2942 2949 2971 2978 3000 3007 3029 3036 3043 3050 3046 3053 3057 3070"/>
